data.description:
Updated, Upgraded and Move-in Ready!  This 2 BR/2BA plus DEN, free-standing home has 1573 SF of living space.  Cozy up to the gas fireplace with stack-stone facade for some ambiance on a chilly Arizona evening.  Above the newer mantel is wiring that is revamped for your wide-screen TV.   Head to the newly remodeled Kitchen for your snack or beverage.  All cabinetry has been replaced so doors and drawers will ''soft-close''.  Island has been reconfigured for a streamlined look.  All kitchen appliances replaced with high-end stainless:  Samsung Refrigerator with French Doors and lower drawer freezer; Samsung electric cooktop range w/convection oven; Bosch dishwasher; & Samsung Microwave.  Counters are a sparkling quartz with textured subway tile backsplash. New 4-TON TRANE HVAC in 2023. Single, deep, stainless sink has a commercial grade faucet/sprayer plus disposal (replaced).  All ductwork was cleaned before owner replaced the HVAC system with a 4-ton TRANE unit from OASIS.  Water Heater replaced with a 50-gallon unit.  All light fixtures, ceiling fans (4), electrical outlets/receptacles were replaced.  Windows are adorned with Levelor Blinds.  Best of all, the flooring was upgraded to Mannington ADURA luxury Vinyl plank which resists water, scratches, and stains.  (No Carpeting!)  Baseboards were replaced, and interior has been freshly painted.  Landscaping was refreshed with new rock/gravel.  So Move In and RELAX!
(GVR Not Available in this area.)
